    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow people to claim unfair dismissal after six months",
        "additional_details": "We believe it is unfair that employees can be dismissed by their employer, but are unable to claim unfair dismissal - in most circumstances - unless they have been working there for at least two years.",
        "background": "We want the Government to give employees the right to claim unfair dismissal after being at the company for 6 months rather than 2 years.",
